    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've absolutely babied this car, keeping it spotless and strictly maintained. It drives like a total dream! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
