    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. All 'Big Three' preventative measures have been addressed: the rod bearings have been replaced with VAC-treated shells, the VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the precise turn-in and lateral grip characteristic of this chassis. The exterior retains a deep luster with no evidence of oxidation, and the cabin is free of common wear points like bolster degradation or pixel failure. This is a superlative example for the collector demanding mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
