    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that transcends the 'used' label. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is deep and glass-like, free from even the smallest stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of pristine leather and untouched trim, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians, ensuring the mechanical performance is as sharp and responsive as the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
