      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in museum-quality condition. The S54 power plant remains the centerpiece, featuring individual throttle bodies that provide instantaneous throttle response and a linear 8,000 RPM power band. This example has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite, including a full VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp, tactile engagement with no synchro-drag, paired with a perfectly calibrated variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry is factory-spec, utilizing fresh bushings and dampers that eliminate any NVH (Noise, Vibration, Harshness). This is a mechanically superlative specimen with zero deferred maintenance, ideal for the purist who values engineering precision.",
